2.2.0 07-Sep-2022
* Switched energy summaries back to using differences of accumulated energy.
  This is more robust to power failure, although less robust to system reset. See the README.
* Changed default port from 8083 to 8000

2.1.0 03-Sep-2022
* Added Matthew's "Seasons" based skin. Called it "SeasonsPower".

2.0.0 05-Aug-2022
* Switch from storing accumulated energy, to delta energies
* Improved output from wee_device --info query.

